TY  - JOUR
TI  - The Nonparametric Approach to Production Analysis
AU  - Varian, Hal R.
AB  - [This paper shows how to test firm demand and supply data for consistency with profit maximization and cost minimization models; test for special restrictions on technology such as constant returns to scale, homotheticity, and separability; recover estimates of the underlying technology; and forecast firm behavior in new situations without making any assumptions concerning the parametric form of underlying production technology.]
C1  - Full publication date: May, 1984
